snippet.title: The Part Of Meghan Markle's Interview That Made Oprah Furious
snippet.description:
Oprah Winfrey’s two-hour interview with Meghan Markle and Prince Harry made a lot of waves when it aired on March 7, 2021.

One of the most shocking moments in the sit-down happened when Markle discussed why the royal family decided not to make her son Archie a prince, which meant he would not receive security detail. When Oprah asked if the royal family had mixed feelings about Archie because of his race, Markle confirmed this, saying that one person had asked questions about what color his skin would be.

Let’s take a look at the part of Meghan Markle’s interview that made Oprah furious.
